 :tx/rationale "Create task: PERF-1: Binary store cache. Serialize loaded Store to .braid/.cache/store.bin (bincode/rmp-serde). On load, if cache is newer than newest txn file, deserialize from cache instead of parsing 6766 EDN files. APPROACH: (1) Add Serialize/Deserialize derives to Store (if not present). (2) In DiskLayout::load_store, check .cache/store.bin mtime vs newest txn file mtime. (3) If cache valid, deserialize directly. If stale, load from txn files, then write cache. (4) Cache invalidation: any new txn file makes cache stale (mtime comparison). ACCEPTANCE: (A) First load: same speed (parses EDN, writes cache). (B) Subsequent loads with no new txns: <0.5s (deserialize only). (C) After new txn: cache invalidated, full parse + re-cache. (D) Cache corruption: graceful fallback to full parse. (E) Store contents identical whether loaded from cache or EDN. FILE: crates/braid/src/layout.rs + crates/braid-kernel/src/store.rs"
